{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-15633/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-15633"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["1:56:33"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["medium shot"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["low"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["fixed"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["two shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["Man and woman look at each other"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-15633/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-15633","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-15633/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-15633"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-15633/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-15633/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-15633/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-15633/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-15633/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-15633/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-15633/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-15633/canvas/1/860782b1-c911-4c85-996e-09de37662020","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T17:19:11.197Z","creator":"Ada ","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>While Reynolds and Alma face each other down, both knowing what the other is doing, the music settles. It’s the calm before the storm.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-15633/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:25.54276315789501,48.163875598085895,302.4521531100477,173.1010765550239"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-15633/canvas/1/5b5161d4-0bcb-420d-89d1-fc2dbf6d41bf","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T17:19:36.444Z","creator":"Ada ","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Reynolds and Alma are seated in the same positions that they were on their <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW231392858 BCX4\" href=\"https://ptannotated.com/items/phan-01637.html\"><u>first</u></a> <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW231392858 BCX4\" href=\"https://ptannotated.com/items/phan-01644.html\"><u>date</u></a>, though this time we see them both in full within the same frame rather than over each other’s shoulders. This shotshows the shift in their power dynamic, as do the events of the scene. While on their first date, it was Reynolds who knew more about the food they ate, correcting her on calling the custard “sauce”;here it is Alma who prepared the food to poison him. He is no longer the one in charge—they have become equals, able to occupy the same space within the frame.</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-15633/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:42.453648325359154,349.6142344497603,1713.8755980861242,610.2721291866027"}}}]}]}]}